title: Campfire Killers - Demo (2001)
description:
Fun country punk. Or something. Existed for a year or two, released a demo and the occasional track from a couple of compilations. Obscure enough for ya?

2. Tribute to a bad man

5. Can't keep an evil man down
6. Evil amigo
